    <p><span class="icon-crice"></span><span class="font-weight-bold">Analytics and customization cookies: </span> cookies collect information we use in aggregate form to help us understand how our websites and services are being used and how effective our marketing campaigns are, and help us customize our websites. If you disable or opt-out of these cookies, you may not be able to use certain features of our websites and services, and it may reduce the support or information that we can provide you.</p>
